reviewText: Even though it is an interview without images, it is interesting the things Dean has to say, however I don't agree with him in a lot of the things he is trying to say..  but for all of you out there, there are better dvd's out there to get.

I expected more documentation and examples of proof.  Instead, I found the DVD to be more about Robert O Dean himself.  He has credentials and he lets you know about the same credentials two or three times. I turned it off about 3/4 through - may return to it to see if I missed anything.
